+ Connect to Kafka\nand Event Hubs
++ Apache Kafka
+++_ format("kafka")
+++_ kafka.bootstrap.servers
+++_ subscribe: topic name
+++_ startingOffsets: latest / earliest
++ Azure Event Hubs (Kafka-compatible)
+++_ Same Kafka connector
+++_ SASL_SSL + PLAIN auth
+++_ Connection string via Databricks Secrets
-- Native Event Hubs Connector
---_ format("eventhubs")
---_ eventhubs.connectionString option
---_ body column (not value)
---_ Consumer group + starting position
-- Message Schema
---_ key, value (binary → cast to string)
---_ topic, partition, offset, timestamp
---_ Parse JSON with from_json()
@endmindmap
